{"tid":557364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首先要訂立標準工時 畀香港人有足夠嘅休息時間","createTime":"2018-02-11T09:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T14:31:15.000Z","uid":64576,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dec55a60d77c1af9c4d4c0ecd8aa223e38e432c6","tid":557364,"uid":64576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T09:39:32.000Z","msg":"香港d老細咁撚度縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n攪到香港打工仔低人工又無足夠休息時間<br />\n人又唔請唔夠 又唔捨得出錢培訓員工<br />\n攪到今次又死人<br />\n<br />\n對上一次深水埗個單就係司機休息唔夠<br />\n所以訂立標準工時勢在必行<br />\n等睇班老細又話成本上升<br />\n你老母啦 員工休息得夠 工作效率會提升架on9<br />\n<br />\n標準工時乜乜柒柒委員會無撚用<br />\n糧就識出 幾十年都仲未攪掂"},{"pid":"3edccf736e378c1688b6d5054d332c6beb6ec138","tid":557364,"uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T09:45:45.000Z","msg":"on9。郁到老細利益既野，政府邊敢做"},{"pid":"1a0fe1debb588688589309c2bd06fae749c3e6fe","tid":557364,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T09:56:02.000Z","msg":"標準工時訂立完後就係減薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7a6025e1d3a46750e8f30847087e58a859cb06","tid":557364,"uid":146535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a0fe1debb588688589309c2bd06fae749c3e6fe","tid":557364,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T09:56:02.000Z","msg":"標準工時訂立完後就係減薪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T09:57:44.000Z","msg":"唔好靠嚇<br />\n佢減左就再做其他<br />\n同埋而家標準工時都過唔到"},{"pid":"5f79abf71d22a7c1a8f050d1c135bb5691cc23ab","tid":557364,"uid":160268,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T09:58:05.000Z","msg":"訂完標準工時<br />\n餐廳要請多咗散工<br />\n最後咪我地消費者食曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b8052344da1040d76ae604de53e35bf6e7d823","tid":557364,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T10:35:31.000Z","msg":"大型公共交通